						<summary>

						<p>On the caves of the central shrine in the Kāḷahastīśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Rājēndra I. Year [3].</p>						

						<p>This inscription commences with the <hi rend="italic">praśasti, Tirumaṉṉi vaḷara</hi>, etc., of Rājēndra I. The date portion is damaged.</p>						

						<p>The purport is not clear as the inscription is badly damaged. It mentions one Rājēndraśōḻaviḷāgam.</p>						

						</summary>
